ason we need these two tools is"},{"start":"107.119","dur":"1.841","text":"because the agent must be able to"},{"start":"108.960","dur":"2.000","text":"actually discover local files and then"},{"start":"110.960","dur":"2.240","text":"run them in Python in order to use this"},{"start":"113.200","dur":"2.160","text":"new approach. And both of these tools"},{"start":"115.360","dur":"2.399","text":"are already available in our framework."},{"start":"117.759","dur":"2.000","text":"So let''s hit send and wait until the"},{"start":"119.759","dur":"2.000","text":"agent is built. Now, I''m also going to"},{"start":"121.759","dur":"2.640","text":"tell it to add another sales ops direct"},{"start":"124.399","dur":"2.961","text":"MCP agent for comparison later. By the"},{"start":"127.360","dur":"1.119","text":"way, if you''re building a more"},{"start":"128.479","dur":"2.321","text":"sophisticated MVP, there is also a new"},{"start":"130.800","dur":"2.320","text":"PRD command which you can use to have"},{"start":"133.120","dur":"2.479","text":"more control over your agent structure."},{"start":"135.599","dur":"1.601","text":"Okay, now here''s where the magic"},{"start":"137.200","dur":"2.480","text":"happens. I added a new special command"},{"start":"139.680","dur":"2.960","text":"called MCP code execution, which you can"},{"start":"142.640","dur":"3.200","text":"use to add MCP servers to an agent using"},{"start":"145.840","dur":"2.160","text":"this new pattern. So all you need to do"},{"start":"148.000","dur":"1.920","text":"in order to use this is simply tag this"},{"start":"149.920","dur":"2.640","text":"command and then tell cursor which MCP"},{"start":"152.560","dur":"2.319","text":"servers to use. So I recommend finding"},{"start":"154.879","dur":"2.561","text":"the exact MCP servers you need on GitHub"},{"start":"157.440","dur":"2.560","text":"or elsewhere and then adding links back"},{"start":"160.000","dur":"2.640","text":"into cursor. Now simply hit send again."},{"start":"162.640","dur":"1.760","text":"So this command already describes to"},{"start":"164.400","dur":"1.760","text":"cursor pretty much everything it needs"},{"start":"166.160","dur":"2.320","text":"to know about this new pattern and even"},{"start":"168.480","dur":"2.080","text":"links the blog post and all the other"},{"start":"170.560","dur":"1.920","text":"resources that it might need. This way"},{"start":"172.480","dur":"2.160","text":"cursor can reliably add it using the"},{"start":"174.640","dur":"1.840","text":"same structure that they proposed in"},{"start":"176.480","dur":"1.839","text":"this blog post. So you can see how now"},{"start":"178.319","dur":"2.241","text":"cursor created the server directory with"},{"start":"180.560","dur":"2.160","text":"the code for our servers and then it"},{"start":"182.720","dur":"1.680","text":"proceeds to creating the code for"},{"start":"184.400","dur":"2.479","text":"individual tools. You might also need to"},{"start":"186.879","dur":"2.321","text":"authenticate the server if it''s using or"},{"start":"189.200","dur":"2.080","text":"off. Now it proceeds to creating files"},{"start":"191.280","dur":"2.560","text":"for individual tools. So you can see how"},{"start":"193.840","dur":"3.119","text":"now this server is made here directly in"},{"start":"196.959","dur":"2.081","text":"code instead of passing this description"},{"start":"199.040","dur":"2.000","text":"and the arguments directly into the"},{"start":"201.040","dur":"2.640","text":"agents context window. Cursor saves this"},{"start":"203.680","dur":"2.479","text":"description in code. So then whenever"},{"start":"206.159","dur":"2.321","text":"our agent needs to use this tool, it"},{"start":"208.480","dur":"2.240","text":"will simply read this file and then it"},{"start":"210.720","dur":"2.320","text":"will see the whole description and the"},{"start":"213.040","dur":"2.400","text":"arguments in order to use this tool. So"},{"start":"215.440","dur":"1.680","text":"this way again we don''t load all the"},{"start":"217.120","dur":"2.560","text":"tools. We only load one tool that cursor"},{"start":"219.680","dur":"2.160","text":"actually needs to use. Okay. So in total"},{"start":"221.840","dur":"2.880","text":"cursor created 15 tools for notion MCP"},{"start":"224.720","dur":"2.239","text":"server and four tools for Google drive."},{"start":"226.959","dur":"2.321","text":"It has also already tested notion MCP"},{"start":"229.280","dur":"2.000","text":"server. However, it wasn''t able to test"},{"start":"231.280","dur":"1.360","text":"Google Drive because of missing"},{"start":"232.640","dur":"1.679","text":"credentials. So make sure you provide"},{"start":"234.319","dur":"1.761","text":"all the credentials up front. Do not"},{"start":"236.080","dur":"1.760","text":"repeat my mistake. Typically you can"},{"start":"237.840","dur":"1.599","text":"find instructions on how to get the"},{"start":"239.439","dur":"1.841","text":"credentials inside the readme of your"},{"start":"241.280","dur":"1.920","text":"MCP server. Then you can simply tell"},{"start":"243.200","dur":"2.239","text":"cursor to retest the server. Then you"},{"start":"245.439","dur":"2.321","text":"will also be required to authenticate."},{"start":"247.760","dur":"1.759","text":"Okay. Now the next step is to write"},{"start":"249.519","dur":"1.440","text":"instructions. So for writing"},{"start":"250.959","dur":"1.681","text":"instructions, I also recommend you use"},{"start":"252.640","dur":"2.080","text":"this write instructions command and then"},{"start":"254.720","dur":"2.000","text":"simply tag the agent that you want to"},{"start":"256.720","dur":"1.919","text":"create the instructions for. Then cursor"},{"start":"258.639","dur":"1.440","text":"is going to ask you a few questions to"},{"start":"260.079","dur":"2.000","text":"properly define the context for your"},{"start":"262.079","dur":"2.001","text":"agent. So make sure you answer all these"},{"start":"264.080","dur":"1.440","text":"questions carefully and the most"},{"start":"265.520","dur":"2.000","text":"important one is the process and"},{"start":"267.520","dur":"2.480","text":"workflow. So prompting is key with this"},{"start":"270.000","dur":"1.840","text":"technique and in order for this agent to"},{"start":"271.840","dur":"2.000","text":"use it effectively, it must clearly"},{"start":"273.840","dur":"2.079","text":"understand the process. So basically the"},{"start":"275.919","dur":"1.840","text":"first step is to always check available"},{"start":"277.759","dur":"2.401","text":"skills in the Mnt skills folder. I''ll"},{"start":"280.160","dur":"2.880","text":"explain why Mnt folder later then it"},{"start":"283.040","dur":"1.840","text":"should use the skill if such a skill is"},{"start":"284.880","dur":"2.400","text":"found for a specific task. If no skills"},{"start":"287.280","dur":"2.400","text":"are found then it should only read one"},{"start":"289.680","dur":"2.160","text":"tool that it needs to use and after that"},{"start":"291.840","dur":"2.079","text":"it should combine all such tools in"},{"start":"293.919","dur":"1.761","text":"order to complete a task successfully"},{"start":"295.680","dur":"2.160","text":"and finally provide suggestions for new"},{"start":"297.840","dur":"2.160","text":"skills to be added. So you can play"},{"start":"300.000","dur":"1.840","text":"around with this workflow. This is just"},{"start":"301.840","dur":"2.400","text":"a general process from the blog post."},{"start":"304.240","dur":"1.200","text":"But I think there are a lot of"},{"start":"305.440","dur":"1.759","text":"innovations just from prompting the"},{"start":"307.199","dur":"2.161","text":"agent. So let''s hit send. And in the"},{"start":"309.360","dur":"2.800","text":"meantime, I also want to add MCPS using"},{"start":"312.160","dur":"2.240","text":"the direct MCP approach to the other"},{"start":"314.400","dur":"3.120","text":"sales ops direct MCP agent. So for this,"},{"start":"317.520","dur":"2.160","text":"we also have a command. It''s simply add"},{"start":"319.680","dur":"1.760","text":"MCP. And then I''m also just going to"},{"start":"321.440","dur":"2.479","text":"link the two MCP servers that we added"},{"start":"323.919","dur":"2.401","text":"to the previous agent. Okay, now we are"},{"start":"326.320","dur":"2.080","text":"ready to test this agency. So let''s open"},{"start":"328.400","dur":"2.000","text":"it in terminal and just run python"},{"start":"330.400","dur":"3.040","text":"agency.py. Pi. Now let''s perform a"},{"start":"333.440","dur":"1.920","text":"simple test. Let me ask it what''s on"},{"start":"335.360","dur":"3.640","text":"this notion page."},{"start":"339.919","dur":"2.000","text":"So first the agent listed the mount"},{"start":"341.919","dur":"3.361","text":"skills directory. Then it read the fetch"},{"start":"345.280","dur":"1.680","text":"tool file to understand all the"},{"start":"346.960","dur":"2.239","text":"parameters. And it seems like it ran"},{"start":"349.199","dur":"3.601","text":"into some issues with the imports."},{"start":"352.800","dur":"1.839","text":"However, then at the end I was still"},{"start":"354.639","dur":"2.801","text":"able to read this page by performing"},{"start":"357.440","dur":"3.039","text":"this fetch tool request and it provided"},{"start":"360.479","dur":"3.041","text":"me with the preview of this file. Okay."},{"start":"363.520","dur":"1.440","text":"Now the next step is to deploy this"},{"start":"364.960","dur":"1.679","text":"agent and then we''ll compare it with the"},{"start":"366.639","dur":"2.321","text":"direct MCP approach. So let''s push our"},{"start":"368.960","dur":"2.160","text":"changes to GitHub and now let''s go to"},{"start":"371.120","dur":"2.560","text":"agency. So hit create new agency and"},{"start":"373.680","dur":"3.200","text":"then find this new agent repo. Then"},{"start":"376.880","dur":"2.240","text":"provide your keys from the end file. And"},{"start":"379.120","dur":"2.000","text":"now let''s wait until our agency is"},{"start":"381.120","dur":"2.400","text":"deployed. Okay. So now our agency is"},{"start":"383.520","dur":"2.480","text":"deployed. So let''s actually test it. So"},{"start":"386.000","dur":"2.479","text":"let me put it in a custom GPT. Let''s"},{"start":"388.479","dur":"2.720","text":"select both agents"},{"start":"391.199","dur":"2.000","text":"and let''s deploy it. Now let me send"},{"start":"393.199","dur":"2.720","text":"this task from Andropics blog post to"},{"start":"395.919","dur":"2.321","text":"copy the transcript from Google Drive"},{"start":"398.240","dur":"2.880","text":"and paste it into a page in notion."},{"start":"401.120","dur":"1.440","text":"Let''s see if it''s actually going to be"},{"start":"402.560","dur":"2.639","text":"able to do it."},{"start":"405.199","dur":"1.921","text":"Seems like it did read way too many"},{"start":"407.120","dur":"1.919","text":"files. Like for example, it even read"},{"start":"409.039","dur":"2.000","text":"this server file which it definitely"},{"start":"411.039","dur":"3.401","text":"doesn''t need."},{"start":"415.680","dur":"2.160","text":"And now finally it tells me that it was"},{"start":"417.840","dur":"2.720","text":"in fact able to do this. So let''s check"},{"start":"420.560","dur":"3.639","text":"the notion page."},{"start":"424.960","dur":"1.600","text":"And yes indeed we now get this"},{"start":"426.560","dur":"2.720","text":"transcript from our Q&A call exactly"},{"start":"429.280","dur":"2.800","text":"like it was on Google Drive. And also at"},{"start":"432.080","dur":"2.160","text":"the end it proposed to create this new"},{"start":"434.240","dur":"2.480","text":"skill for itself. So let me tell it to"},{"start":"436.720","dur":"1.840","text":"save the skill. So you can see that the"},{"start":"438.560","dur":"1.919","text":"agent told me that it saved the skills"},{"start":"440.479","dur":"2.560","text":"in the mount skills directory. So the"},{"start":"443.039","dur":"1.521","text":"reason you need to use this mount"},{"start":"444.560","dur":"1.520","text":"directory is because we now have"},{"start":"446.080","dur":"2.720","text":"persistent storage on our platform. And"},{"start":"448.800","dur":"1.600","text":"without this feature, it would not be"},{"start":"450.400","dur":"2.160","text":"possible to allow your agents to evolve"},{"start":"452.560","dur":"2.400","text":"and build their own skills over time. So"},{"start":"454.960","dur":"2.239","text":"in this mount directory essentially your"},{"start":"457.199","dur":"2.321","text":"agents can now save files like this and"},{"start":"459.520","dur":"2.160","text":"reference them across different chats."},{"start":"461.680","dur":"2.079","text":"So now if I start a new chat and then"},{"start":"463.759","dur":"2.160","text":"send the same prompt again, the agent"},{"start":"465.919","dur":"2.321","text":"should take a lot less time and just use"},{"start":"468.240","dur":"2.000","text":"the skill in order to do this task"},{"start":"470.240","dur":"2.079","text":"quickly. So you can see how now it found"},{"start":"472.319","dur":"2.481","text":"the skill and read the file and the"},{"start":"474.800","dur":"2.079","text":"agent was able to still perform the same"},{"start":"476.879","dur":"1.760","text":"task."},{"start":"478.639","dur":"2.000","text":"Okay, now let''s quickly test another"},{"start":"480.639","dur":"3.441","text":"agent that uses direct MCP approach. So"},{"start":"484.080","dur":"1.760","text":"now you can see how this agent is"},{"start":"485.840","dur":"1.840","text":"reading this whole transcript with the G"},{"start":"487.680","dur":"2.560","text":"drive read file tool which hopefully is"},{"start":"490.240","dur":"2.560","text":"not going to cost me too much and it"},{"start":"492.800","dur":"2.480","text":"also read the notion page and now it''s"},{"start":"495.280","dur":"1.919","text":"trying to add this transcript to this"},{"start":"497.199","dur":"2.081","text":"notion page. But as you can see it has"},{"start":"499.280","dur":"2.639","text":"to manually type this whole thing which"},{"start":"501.919","dur":"1.921","text":"is definitely going to cost me too much"},{"start":"503.840","dur":"2.880","text":"now. So you can see how it''s literally"},{"start":"506.720","dur":"2.000","text":"spending like probably tens of thousands"},{"start":"508.720","dur":"2.319","text":"of tokens for no reason simply because"},{"start":"511.039","dur":"2.560","text":"it had to do one simple copy paste"},{"start":"513.599","dur":"2.961","text":"operation. Finally, it''s finished. So"},{"start":"516.560","dur":"2.240","text":"now let''s take a look at the traces and"},{"start":"518.800","dur":"2.479","text":"analyze the costs. So tracing is enabled"},{"start":"521.279","dur":"2.320","text":"by default in our framework. And in"},{"start":"523.599","dur":"1.441","text":"order to see the traces, all you need to"},{"start":"525.040","dur":"2.160","text":"do is go to dashboard and then simply"},{"start":"527.200","dur":"2.720","text":"find the name of your agency. Okay, so"},{"start":"529.920","dur":"2.960","text":"let''s see this sales ops direct MCP"},{"start":"532.880","dur":"2.720","text":"agent. And in total, this agent consumed"},{"start":"535.600","dur":"3.679","text":"32,000 tokens. This is just insane. And"},{"start":"539.279","dur":"1.921","text":"most of these tokens aren''t even input"},{"start":"541.200","dur":"1.920","text":"tokens. It''s also a lot of output"},{"start":"543.120","dur":"2.240","text":"tokens, which are extremely expensive."},{"start":"545.360","dur":"1.599","text":"And with this new approach, the amount"},{"start":"546.959","dur":"3.440","text":"of tokens is only 12,000, which is a lot"},{"start":"550.399","dur":"2.321","text":"less, although it''s still quite a bit."},{"start":"552.720","dur":"1.440","text":"And I think the reason this is still"},{"start":"554.160","dur":"1.920","text":"consumes so many tokens is because this"},{"start":"556.080","dur":"2.319","text":"agent, as you can see, just performs way"},{"start":"558.399","dur":"2.481","text":"too many unnecessary tool calls. But I"},{"start":"560.880","dur":"1.680","text":"do think that it''s completely possible"},{"start":"562.560","dur":"2.719","text":"to optimize it with more prompting. And"},{"start":"565.279","dur":"2.161","text":"when the agent used one of the existing"},{"start":"567.440","dur":"3.200","text":"skills, it only consumed 4,000 tokens to"},{"start":"570.640","dur":"2.160","text":"perform the same task, which is now"},{"start":"572.800","dur":"3.520","text":"around 10 times less. So in conclusion,"},{"start":"575.000","dur":"113.000"},{"start":"576.320","dur":"2.160","text":"I believe this approach is extremely"},{"start":"578.480","dur":"2.479","text":"powerful, but as they say, with great"},{"start":"580.959","dur":"2.721","text":"power comes great responsibility. While"},{"start":"583.680","dur":"1.680","text":"I was definitely able to reduce the"},{"start":"585.360","dur":"1.840","text":"token consumption from the intermediate"},{"start":"587.200","dur":"2.480","text":"tool outputs, the agent still consumed"},{"start":"589.680","dur":"1.839","text":"more tokens than it should have when"},{"start":"591.519","dur":"2.801","text":"calling the tools. It executed code way"},{"start":"594.320","dur":"1.840","text":"too many times. It read way too many"},{"start":"596.160","dur":"2.000","text":"unnecessary files and it just took too"},{"start":"598.160","dur":"1.840","text":"long to perform a simple task on the"},{"start":"600.000","dur":"2.480","text":"first attempt. However, the agent was"},{"start":"602.480","dur":"2.240","text":"still able to save a lot more tokens"},{"start":"604.720","dur":"2.880","text":"compared to the old direct MCP approach."},{"start":"607.600","dur":"1.760","text":"Additionally, it was even able to"},{"start":"609.360","dur":"2.400","text":"self-improve by creating a new skill"},{"start":"611.760","dur":"1.759","text":"which cut down the number of code"},{"start":"613.519","dur":"3.041","text":"executions in subsequent runs. So, my"},{"start":"616.560","dur":"2.800","text":"final verdict is yes, this approach is"},{"start":"619.360","dur":"2.080","text":"ready for production, but it requires"},{"start":"621.440","dur":"3.200","text":"proper prompting. Prompting here is key."},{"start":"624.640","dur":"2.160","text":"While the LLMs aren''t trained for this"},{"start":"626.800","dur":"2.000","text":"new method yet, you have to carefully"},{"start":"628.800","dur":"2.159","text":"describe how to use this new pattern,"},{"start":"630.959","dur":"1.601","text":"otherwise they''re going to make a lot of"},{"start":"632.560","dur":"2.160","text":"mistakes. But if you do it right, and"},{"start":"634.720","dur":"1.600","text":"I''m sure many of you will, with this"},{"start":"636.320","dur":"2.400","text":"repo, the benefits far outweigh the"},{"start":"638.720","dur":"2.239","text":"costs. You get way more autonomy and"},{"start":"640.959","dur":"2.721","text":"flexibility with only a minor drop in"},{"start":"643.680","dur":"2.719","text":"reliability. So yes, this is the new"},{"start":"646.399","dur":"2.721","text":"paradigm. Just let your agents run the"},{"start":"649.120","dur":"3.040","text":"code. We no longer have to create these"},{"start":"652.160","dur":"1.280","text":"abstractions on top of other"},{"start":"653.440","dur":"2.000","text":"abstractions because agents can just"},{"start":"655.440","dur":"2.160","text":"generate the code to do whatever they"},{"start":"657.600","dur":"2.720","text":"need by themselves. However, don''t use"},{"start":"660.320","dur":"1.840","text":"it for simple agents like customer"},{"start":"662.160","dur":"2.400","text":"support. save it for more sophisticated"},{"start":"664.560","dur":"2.719","text":"general agents like analytics, research,"},{"start":"667.279","dur":"2.481","text":"or operations. For simple agents, it"},{"start":"669.760","dur":"1.519","text":"still doesn''t make sense. And when"},{"start":"671.279","dur":"1.601","text":"you''re ready to deploy this, check out"},{"start":"672.880","dur":"1.840","text":"our platform because infrastructure"},{"start":"674.720","dur":"1.600","text":"overhead is actually the biggest"},{"start":"676.320","dur":"2.240","text":"downside of this approach. And we''re the"},{"start":"678.560","dur":"1.600","text":"only platform on the market that"},{"start":"680.160","dur":"1.919","text":"supports everything you need to run this"},{"start":"682.079","dur":"2.241","text":"out of the box. More advanced EI agent"},{"start":"684.320","dur":"1.519","text":"templates are coming on this channel"},{"start":"685.839","dur":"2.560","text":"soon."}]}}','2025-11-13T21:03:00.990Z');
INSERT INTO "mcp_actions" VALUES('a857c399-3438-4ecd-9d3e-5b303f2addae','5dd28c5e-208f-4d10-902c-c6eb0fd17f10','youtube-transcript','get_youtube_transcript',3,1,NULL,NULL,'{"params":{"videoUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fg8VHXr-WVM"},"result":{"data":[{"start":"0.000","dur":"45.000"},{"start":"0.080","dur":"2.240","text":"In my last video, I showed a new method"},{"start":"2.320","dur":"2.880","text":"proposed by Anthropic called MCP code"},{"start":"5.200","dur":"2.559","text":"execution. This technique is the future"},{"start":"7.759","dur":"2.481","text":"of building AI agents because it reduces"},{"start":"10.240","dur":"3.680","text":"token consumption 98% while giving your"},{"start":"13.920","dur":"2.880","text":"agents way more autonomy and flexibility"},{"start":"16.800","dur":"2.559","text":"to evolve their own skills. In this"},{"start":"19.359","dur":"1.920","text":"video, I''ll build this life with you"},{"start":"21.279","dur":"2.080","text":"step by step. I''ll compare this new"},{"start":"23.359","dur":"2.481","text":"approach with the old direct MCP method"},{"start":"25.840","dur":"1.920","text":"and give you the final repo plus a"},{"start":"27.760","dur":"2.800","text":"template to convert any MCP server to"},{"start":"30.560","dur":"2.400","text":"this new pattern. At the end, I''ll also"},{"start":"32.960","dur":"2.160","text":"share whether this is actually ready for"},{"start":"35.120","dur":"2.400","text":"production or not. Before you watch this"},{"start":"37.520","dur":"1.760","text":"video, make sure you watch the previous"},{"start":"39.280","dur":"2.160","text":"one to fully understand all the theory"},{"start":"41.440","dur":"2.720","text":"behind this new method. Let''s dive right"},{"start":"44.160","dur":"2.239","text":"in. So the agent that we will build"},{"start":"45.000","dur":"530.000"},{"start":"46.399","dur":"2.401","text":"today is the sales operations agent from"},{"start":"48.800","dur":"2.160","text":"Antropics blog post that can read"},{"start":"50.960","dur":"1.840","text":"meeting transcripts and then attach them"},{"start":"52.800","dur":"2.800","text":"into your CRM without actually reading"},{"start":"55.600","dur":"2.080","text":"the contents of the file. The"},{"start":"57.680","dur":"1.600","text":"architecture for this agent is pretty"},{"start":"59.280","dur":"1.840","text":"simple. It''s just one agent with this"},{"start":"61.120","dur":"2.079","text":"code execution tool that connects to"},{"start":"63.199","dur":"2.960","text":"Google Drive MCP and Notion MCP because"},{"start":"66.159","dur":"2.721","text":"our CRM is in notion. So in order to get"},{"start":"68.880","dur":"1.919","text":"started, you need to copy our starter"},{"start":"70.799","dur":"2.241","text":"template which will now contain a new"},{"start":"73.040","dur":"2.880","text":"special command to use this new pattern."},{"start":"75.920","dur":"1.920","text":"Make sure to set visibility to private"},{"start":"77.840","dur":"2.720","text":"and then open this repo in cursor. So I"},{"start":"80.560","dur":"2.000","text":"will be building this in cursor, but you"},{"start":"82.560","dur":"2.879","text":"can also use cloud codeex or any other"},{"start":"85.439","dur":"2.241","text":"AI coding agent that you prefer. The"},{"start":"87.680","dur":"1.280","text":"only thing you need to do if you''re not"},{"start":"88.960","dur":"2.560","text":"using cursor is to simply tag this"},{"start":"91.520","dur":"2.480","text":"workflow file and the commands files"},{"start":"94.000","dur":"2.320","text":"that we''ll be using in the prompt. So"},{"start":"96.320","dur":"1.839","text":"I''m going to start simple and just tell"},{"start":"98.159","dur":"2.801","text":"cloudset to create a sales ops agent"},{"start":"100.960","dur":"2.159","text":"with two built-in tools IPython"},{"start":"103.119","dur":"2.161","text":"interpreter and persistent shell tool."},{"start":"105.280","dur":"1.839","text":"The reason we need these two tools is"},{"start":"107.119","dur":"1.841","text":"because the agent must be able to"},{"start":"108.960","dur":"2.000","text":"actually discover local files and then"},{"start":"110.960","dur":"2.240","text":"run them in Python in order to use this"},{"start":"113.200","dur":"2.160","text":"new approach. And both of these tools"},{"start":"115.360","dur":"2.399","text":"are already available in our framework."},{"start":"117.759","dur":"2.000","text":"So let''s hit send and wait until the"},{"start":"119.759","dur":"2.000","text":"agent is built. Now, I''m also going to"},{"start":"121.759","dur":"2.640","text":"tell it to add another sales ops direct"},{"start":"124.399","dur":"2.961","text":"MCP agent for comparison later. By the"},{"start":"127.360","dur":"1.119","text":"way, if you''re building a more"},{"start":"128.479","dur":"2.321","text":"sophisticated MVP, there is also a new"},{"start":"130.800","dur":"2.320","text":"PRD command which you can use to have"},{"start":"133.120","dur":"2.479","text":"more control over your agent structure."},{"start":"135.599","dur":"1.601","text":"Okay, now here''s where the magic"},{"start":"137.200","dur":"2.480","text":"happens. I added a new special command"},{"start":"139.680","dur":"2.960","text":"called MCP code execution, which you can"},{"start":"142.640","dur":"3.200","text":"use to add MCP servers to an agent using"},{"start":"145.840","dur":"2.160","text":"this new pattern. So all you need to do"},{"start":"148.000","dur":"1.920","text":"in order to use this is simply tag this"},{"start":"149.920","dur":"2.640","text":"command and then tell cursor which MCP"},{"start":"152.560","dur":"2.319","text":"servers to use. So I recommend finding"},{"start":"154.879","dur":"2.561","text":"the exact MCP servers you need on GitHub"},{"start":"157.440","dur":"2.560","text":"or elsewhere and then adding links back"},{"start":"160.000","dur":"2.640","text":"into cursor. Now simply hit send again."},{"start":"162.640","dur":"1.760","text":"So this command already describes to"},{"start":"164.400","dur":"1.760","text":"cursor pretty much everything it needs"},{"start":"166.160","dur":"2.320","text":"to know about this new pattern and even"},{"start":"168.480","dur":"2.080","text":"links the blog post and all the other"},{"start":"170.560","dur":"1.920","text":"resources that it might need. This way"},{"start":"172.480","dur":"2.160","text":"cursor can reliably add it using the"},{"start":"174.640","dur":"1.840","text":"same structure that they proposed in"},{"start":"176.480","dur":"1.839","text":"this blog post. So you can see how now"},{"start":"178.319","dur":"2.241","text":"cursor created the server directory with"},{"start":"180.560","dur":"2.160","text":"the code for our servers and then it"},{"start":"182.720","dur":"1.680","text":"proceeds to creating the code for"},{"start":"184.400","dur":"2.479","text":"individual tools. You might also need to"},{"start":"186.879","dur":"2.321","text":"authenticate the server if it''s using or"},{"start":"189.200","dur":"2.080","text":"off. Now it proceeds to creating files"},{"start":"191.280","dur":"2.560","text":"for individual tools. So you can see how"},{"start":"193.840","dur":"3.119","text":"now this server is made here directly in"},{"start":"196.959","dur":"2.081","text":"code instead of passing this description"},{"start":"199.040","dur":"2.000","text":"and the arguments directly into the"},{"start":"201.040","dur":"2.640","text":"agents context window. Cursor saves this"},{"start":"203.680","dur":"2.479","text":"description in code. So then whenever"},{"start":"206.159","dur":"2.321","text":"our agent needs to use this tool, it"},{"start":"208.480","dur":"2.240","text":"will simply read this file and then it"},{"start":"210.720","dur":"2.320","text":"will see the whole description and the"},{"start":"213.040","dur":"2.400","text":"arguments in order to use this tool. So"},{"start":"215.440","dur":"1.680","text":"this way again we don''t load all the"},{"start":"217.120","dur":"2.560","text":"tools. We only load one tool that cursor"},{"start":"219.680","dur":"2.160","text":"actually needs to use. Okay. So in total"},{"start":"221.840","dur":"2.880","text":"cursor created 15 tools for notion MCP"},{"start":"224.720","dur":"2.239","text":"server and four tools for Google drive."},{"start":"226.959","dur":"2.321","text":"It has also already tested notion MCP"},{"start":"229.280","dur":"2.000","text":"server. However, it wasn''t able to test"},{"start":"231.280","dur":"1.360","text":"Google Drive because of missing"},{"start":"232.640","dur":"1.679","text":"credentials. So make sure you provide"},{"start":"234.319","dur":"1.761","text":"all the credentials up front. Do not"},{"start":"236.080","dur":"1.760","text":"repeat my mistake. Typically you can"},{"start":"237.840","dur":"1.599","text":"find instructions on how to get the"},{"start":"239.439","dur":"1.841","text":"credentials inside the readme of your"},{"start":"241.280","dur":"1.920","text":"MCP server. Then you can simply tell"},{"start":"243.200","dur":"2.239","text":"cursor to retest the server. Then you"},{"start":"245.439","dur":"2.321","text":"will also be required to authenticate."},{"start":"247.760","dur":"1.759","text":"Okay. Now the next step is to write"},{"start":"249.519","dur":"1.440","text":"instructions. So for writing"},{"start":"250.959","dur":"1.681","text":"instructions, I also recommend you use"},{"start":"252.640","dur":"2.080","text":"this write instructions command and then"},{"start":"254.720","dur":"2.000","text":"simply tag the agent that you want to"},{"start":"256.720","dur":"1.919","text":"create the instructions for. Then cursor"},{"start":"258.639","dur":"1.440","text":"is going to ask you a few questions to"},{"start":"260.079","dur":"2.000","text":"properly define the context for your"},{"start":"262.079","dur":"2.001","text":"agent. So make sure you answer all these"},{"start":"264.080","dur":"1.440","text":"questions carefully and the most"},{"start":"265.520","dur":"2.000","text":"important one is the process and"},{"start":"267.520","dur":"2.480","text":"workflow. So prompting is key with this"},{"start":"270.000","dur":"1.840","text":"technique and in order for this agent to"},{"start":"271.840","dur":"2.000","text":"use it effectively, it must clearly"},{"start":"273.840","dur":"2.079","text":"understand the process. So basically the"},{"start":"275.919","dur":"1.840","text":"first step is to always check available"},{"start":"277.759","dur":"2.401","text":"skills in the Mnt skills folder. I''ll"},{"start":"280.160","dur":"2.880","text":"explain why Mnt folder later then it"},{"start":"283.040","dur":"1.840","text":"should use the skill if such a skill is"},{"start":"284.880","dur":"2.400","text":"found for a specific task. If no skills"},{"start":"287.280","dur":"2.400","text":"are found then it should only read one"},{"start":"289.680","dur":"2.160","text":"tool that it needs to use and after that"},{"start":"291.840","dur":"2.079","text":"it should combine all such tools in"},{"start":"293.919","dur":"1.761","text":"order to complete a task successfully"},{"start":"295.680","dur":"2.160","text":"and finally provide suggestions for new"},{"start":"297.840","dur":"2.160","text":"skills to be added. So you can play"},{"start":"300.000","dur":"1.840","text":"around with this workflow. This is just"},{"start":"301.840","dur":"2.400","text":"a general process from the blog post."},{"start":"304.240","dur":"1.200","text":"But I think there are a lot of"},{"start":"305.440","dur":"1.759","text":"innovations just from prompting the"},{"start":"307.199","dur":"2.161","text":"agent. So let''s hit send. And in the"},{"start":"309.360","dur":"2.800","text":"meantime, I also want to add MCPS using"},{"start":"312.160","dur":"2.240","text":"the direct MCP approach to the other"},{"start":"314.400","dur":"3.120","text":"sales ops direct MCP agent. So for this,"},{"start":"317.520","dur":"2.160","text":"we also have a command. It''s simply add"},{"start":"319.680","dur":"1.760","text":"MCP. And then I''m also just going to"},{"start":"321.440","dur":"2.479","text":"link the two MCP servers that we added"},{"start":"323.919","dur":"2.401","text":"to the previous agent. Okay, now we are"},{"start":"326.320","dur":"2.080","text":"ready to test this agency. So let''s open"},{"start":"328.400","dur":"2.000","text":"it in terminal and just run python"},{"start":"330.400","dur":"3.040","text":"agency.py. Pi. Now let''s perform a"},{"start":"333.440","dur":"1.920","text":"simple test. Let me ask it what''s on"},{"start":"335.360","dur":"3.640","text":"this notion page."},{"start":"339.919","dur":"2.000","text":"So first the agent listed the mount"},{"start":"341.919","dur":"3.361","text":"skills directory. Then it read the fetch"},{"start":"345.280","dur":"1.680","text":"tool file to understand all the"},{"start":"346.960","dur":"2.239","text":"parameters. And it seems like it ran"},{"start":"349.199","dur":"3.601","text":"into some issues with the imports."},{"start":"352.800","dur":"1.839","text":"However, then at the end I was still"},{"start":"354.639","dur":"2.801","text":"able to read this page by performing"},{"start":"357.440","dur":"3.039","text":"this fetch tool request and it provided"},{"start":"360.479","dur":"3.041","text":"me with the preview of this file. Okay."},{"start":"363.520","dur":"1.440","text":"Now the next step is to deploy this"},{"start":"364.960","dur":"1.679","text":"agent and then we''ll compare it with the"},{"start":"366.639","dur":"2.321","text":"direct MCP approach. So let''s push our"},{"start":"368.960","dur":"2.160","text":"changes to GitHub and now let''s go to"},{"start":"371.120","dur":"2.560","text":"agency. So hit create new agency and"},{"start":"373.680","dur":"3.200","text":"then find this new agent repo. Then"},{"start":"376.880","dur":"2.240","text":"provide your keys from the end file. And"},{"start":"379.120","dur":"2.000","text":"now let''s wait until our agency is"},{"start":"381.120","dur":"2.400","text":"deployed. Okay. So now our agency is"},{"start":"383.520","dur":"2.480","text":"deployed. So let''s actually test it. So"},{"start":"386.000","dur":"2.479","text":"let me put it in a custom GPT. Let''s"},{"start":"388.479","dur":"2.720","text":"select both agents"},{"start":"391.199","dur":"2.000","text":"and let''s deploy it. Now let me send"},{"start":"393.199","dur":"2.720","text":"this task from Andropics blog post to"},{"start":"395.919","dur":"2.321","text":"copy the transcript from Google Drive"},{"start":"398.240","dur":"2.880","text":"and paste it into a page in notion."},{"start":"401.120","dur":"1.440","text":"Let''s see if it''s actually going to be"},{"start":"402.560","dur":"2.639","text":"able to do it."},{"start":"405.199","dur":"1.921","text":"Seems like it did read way too many"},{"start":"407.120","dur":"1.919","text":"files. Like for example, it even read"},{"start":"409.039","dur":"2.000","text":"this server file which it definitely"},{"start":"411.039","dur":"3.401","text":"doesn''t need."},{"start":"415.680","dur":"2.160","text":"And now finally it tells me that it was"},{"start":"417.840","dur":"2.720","text":"in fact able to do this. So let''s check"},{"start":"420.560","dur":"3.639","text":"the notion page."},{"start":"424.960","dur":"1.600","text":"And yes indeed we now get this"},{"start":"426.560","dur":"2.720","text":"transcript from our Q&A call exactly"},{"start":"429.280","dur":"2.800","text":"like it was on Google Drive. And also at"},{"start":"432.080","dur":"2.160","text":"the end it proposed to create this new"},{"start":"434.240","dur":"2.480","text":"skill for itself. So let me tell it to"},{"start":"436.720","dur":"1.840","text":"save the skill. So you can see that the"},{"start":"438.560","dur":"1.919","text":"agent told me that it saved the skills"},{"start":"440.479","dur":"2.560","text":"in the mount skills directory. So the"},{"start":"443.039","dur":"1.521","text":"reason you need to use this mount"},{"start":"444.560","dur":"1.520","text":"directory is because we now have"},{"start":"446.080","dur":"2.720","text":"persistent storage on our platform. And"},{"start":"448.800","dur":"1.600","text":"without this feature, it would not be"},{"start":"450.400","dur":"2.160","text":"possible to allow your agents to evolve"},{"start":"452.560","dur":"2.400","text":"and build their own skills over time. So"},{"start":"454.960","dur":"2.239","text":"in this mount directory essentially your"},{"start":"457.199","dur":"2.321","text":"agents can now save files like this and"},{"start":"459.520","dur":"2.160","text":"reference them across different chats."},{"start":"461.680","dur":"2.079","text":"So now if I start a new chat and then"},{"start":"463.759","dur":"2.160","text":"send the same prompt again, the agent"},{"start":"465.919","dur":"2.321","text":"should take a lot less time and just use"},{"start":"468.240","dur":"2.000","text":"the skill in order to do this task"},{"start":"470.240","dur":"2.079","text":"quickly. So you can see how now it found"},{"start":"472.319","dur":"2.481","text":"the skill and read the file and the"},{"start":"474.800","dur":"2.079","text":"agent was able to still perform the same"},{"start":"476.879","dur":"1.760","text":"task."},{"start":"478.639","dur":"2.000","text":"Okay, now let''s quickly test another"},{"start":"480.639","dur":"3.441","text":"agent that uses direct MCP approach. So"},{"start":"484.080","dur":"1.760","text":"now you can see how this agent is"},{"start":"485.840","dur":"1.840","text":"reading this whole transcript with the G"},{"start":"487.680","dur":"2.560","text":"drive read file tool which hopefully is"},{"start":"490.240","dur":"2.560","text":"not going to cost me too much and it"},{"start":"492.800","dur":"2.480","text":"also read the notion page and now it''s"},{"start":"495.280","dur":"1.919","text":"trying to add this transcript to this"},{"start":"497.199","dur":"2.081","text":"notion page. But as you can see it has"},{"start":"499.280","dur":"2.639","text":"to manually type this whole thing which"},{"start":"501.919","dur":"1.921","text":"is definitely going to cost me too much"},{"start":"503.840","dur":"2.880","text":"now. So you can see how it''s literally"},{"start":"506.720","dur":"2.000","text":"spending like probably tens of thousands"},{"start":"508.720","dur":"2.319","text":"of tokens for no reason simply because"},{"start":"511.039","dur":"2.560","text":"it had to do one simple copy paste"},{"start":"513.599","dur":"2.961","text":"operation. Finally, it''s finished. So"},{"start":"516.560","dur":"2.240","text":"now let''s take a look at the traces and"},{"start":"518.800","dur":"2.479","text":"analyze the costs. So tracing is enabled"},{"start":"521.279","dur":"2.320","text":"by default in our framework. And in"},{"start":"523.599","dur":"1.441","text":"order to see the traces, all you need to"},{"start":"525.040","dur":"2.160","text":"do is go to dashboard and then simply"},{"start":"527.200","dur":"2.720","text":"find the name of your agency. Okay, so"},{"start":"529.920","dur":"2.960","text":"let''s see this sales ops direct MCP"},{"start":"532.880","dur":"2.720","text":"agent. And in total, this agent consumed"},{"start":"535.600","dur":"3.679","text":"32,000 tokens. This is just insane. And"},{"start":"539.279","dur":"1.921","text":"most of these tokens aren''t even input"},{"start":"541.200","dur":"1.920","text":"tokens. It''s also a lot of output"},{"start":"543.120","dur":"2.240","text":"tokens, which are extremely expensive."},{"start":"545.360","dur":"1.599","text":"And with this new approach, the amount"},{"start":"546.959","dur":"3.440","text":"of tokens is only 12,000, which is a lot"},{"start":"550.399","dur":"2.321","text":"less, although it''s still quite a bit."},{"start":"552.720","dur":"1.440","text":"And I think the reason this is still"},{"start":"554.160","dur":"1.920","text":"consumes so many tokens is because this"},{"start":"556.080","dur":"2.319","text":"agent, as you can see, just performs way"},{"start":"558.399","dur":"2.481","text":"too many unnecessary tool calls. But I"},{"start":"560.880","dur":"1.680","text":"do think that it''s completely possible"},{"start":"562.560","dur":"2.719","text":"to optimize it with more prompting. And"},{"start":"565.279","dur":"2.161","text":"when the agent used one of the existing"},{"start":"567.440","dur":"3.200","text":"skills, it only consumed 4,000 tokens to"},{"start":"570.640","dur":"2.160","text":"perform the same task, which is now"},{"start":"572.800","dur":"3.520","text":"around 10 times less. So in conclusion,"},{"start":"575.000","dur":"113.000"},{"start":"576.320","dur":"2.160","text":"I believe this approach is extremely"},{"start":"578.480","dur":"2.479","text":"powerful, but as they say, with great"},{"start":"580.959","dur":"2.721","text":"power comes great responsibility. While"},{"start":"583.680","dur":"1.680","text":"I was definitely able to reduce the"},{"start":"585.360","dur":"1.840","text":"token consumption from the intermediate"},{"start":"587.200","dur":"2.480","text":"tool outputs, the agent still consumed"},{"start":"589.680","dur":"1.839","text":"more tokens than it should have when"},{"start":"591.519","dur":"2.801","text":"calling the tools. It executed code way"},{"start":"594.320","dur":"1.840","text":"too many times. It read way too many"},{"start":"596.160","dur":"2.000","text":"unnecessary files and it just took too"},{"start":"598.160","dur":"1.840","text":"long to perform a simple task on the"},{"start":"600.000","dur":"2.480","text":"first attempt. However, the agent was"},{"start":"602.480","dur":"2.240","text":"still able to save a lot more tokens"},{"start":"604.720","dur":"2.880","text":"compared to the old direct MCP approach."},{"start":"607.600","dur":"1.760","text":"Additionally, it was even able to"},{"start":"609.360","dur":"2.400","text":"self-improve by creating a new skill"},{"start":"611.760","dur":"1.759","text":"which cut down the number of code"},{"start":"613.519","dur":"3.041","text":"executions in subsequent runs. So, my"},{"start":"616.560","dur":"2.800","text":"final verdict is yes, this approach is"},{"start":"619.360","dur":"2.080","text":"ready for production, but it requires"},{"start":"621.440","dur":"3.200","text":"proper prompting. Prompting here is key."},{"start":"624.640","dur":"2.160","text":"While the LLMs aren''t trained for this"},{"start":"626.800","dur":"2.000","text":"new method yet, you have to carefully"},{"start":"628.800","dur":"2.159","text":"describe how to use this new pattern,"},{"start":"630.959","dur":"1.601","text":"otherwise they''re going to make a lot of"},{"start":"632.560","dur":"2.160","text":"mistakes. But if you do it right, and"},{"start":"634.720","dur":"1.600","text":"I''m sure many of you will, with this"},{"start":"636.320","dur":"2.400","text":"repo, the benefits far outweigh the"},{"start":"638.720","dur":"2.239","text":"costs. You get way more autonomy and"},{"start":"640.959","dur":"2.721","text":"flexibility with only a minor drop in"},{"start":"643.680","dur":"2.719","text":"reliability. So yes, this is the new"},{"start":"646.399","dur":"2.721","text":"paradigm. Just let your agents run the"},{"start":"649.120","dur":"3.040","text":"code. We no longer have to create these"},{"start":"652.160","dur":"1.280","text":"abstractions on top of other"},{"start":"653.440","dur":"2.000","text":"abstractions because agents can just"},{"start":"655.440","dur":"2.160","text":"generate the code to do whatever they"},{"start":"657.600","dur":"2.720","text":"need by themselves. However, don''t use"},{"start":"660.320","dur":"1.840","text":"it for simple agents like customer"},{"start":"662.160","dur":"2.400","text":"support. save it for more sophisticated"},{"start":"664.560","dur":"2.719","text":"general agents like analytics, research,"},{"start":"667.279","dur":"2.481","text":"or operations. For simple agents, it"},{"start":"669.760","dur":"1.519","text":"still doesn''t make sense. And when"},{"start":"671.279","dur":"1.601","text":"you''re ready to deploy this, check out"},{"start":"672.880","dur":"1.840","text":"our platform because infrastructure"},{"start":"674.720","dur":"1.600","text":"overhead is actually the biggest"},{"start":"676.320","dur":"2.240","text":"downside of this approach. And we''re the"},{"start":"678.560","dur":"1.600","text":"only platform on the market that"},{"start":"680.160","dur":"1.919","text":"supports everything you need to run this"},{"start":"682.079","dur":"2.241","text":"out of the box. More advanced EI agent"},{"start":"684.320","dur":"1.519","text":"templates are coming on this channel"},{"start":"685.839","dur":"2.560","text":"soon."}]}}','2025-11-13T21:15:45.705Z');
INSERT INTO "mcp_actions" VALUES('da53bf2b-9fbc-4b53-b53b-19eba38a76fb','5dd28c5e-208f-4d10-902c-c6eb0fd17f10','youtube-transcript','get_youtube_transcript',3,1,NULL,NULL,'{"params":{"videoUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fg8VHXr-WVM"},"result":{"data":[{"start":"0.000","dur":"45.000"},{"start":"0.080","dur":"2.240","text":"In my last video, I showed a new method"},{"start":"2.320","dur":"2.880","text":"proposed by Anthropic called MCP code"},{"start":"5.200","dur":"2.559","text":"execution. This technique is the future"},{"start":"7.759","dur":"2.481","text":"of building AI agents because it reduces"},{"start":"10.240","dur":"3.680","text":"token consumption 98% while giving your"},{"start":"13.920","dur":"2.880","text":"agents way more autonomy and flexibility"},{"start":"16.800","dur":"2.559","text":"to evolve their own skills. In this"},{"start":"19.359","dur":"1.920","text":"video, I''ll build this life with you"},{"start":"21.279","dur":"2.080","text":"step by step. I''ll compare this new"},{"start":"23.359","dur":"2.481","text":"approach with the old direct MCP method"},{"start":"25.840","dur":"1.920","text":"and give you the final repo plus a"},{"start":"27.760","dur":"2.800","text":"template to convert any MCP server to"},{"start":"30.560","dur":"2.400","text":"this new pattern. At the end, I''ll also"},{"start":"32.960","dur":"2.160","text":"share whether this is actually ready for"},{"start":"35.120","dur":"2.400","text":"production or not. Before you watch this"},{"start":"37.520","dur":"1.760","text":"video, make sure you watch the previous"},{"start":"39.280","dur":"2.160","text":"one to fully understand all the theory"},{"start":"41.440","dur":"2.720","text":"behind this new method. Let''s dive right"},{"start":"44.160","dur":"2.239","text":"in. So the agent that we will build"},{"start":"45.000","dur":"530.000"},{"start":"46.399","dur":"2.401","text":"today is the sales operations agent from"},{"start":"48.800","dur":"2.160","text":"Antropics blog post that can read"},{"start":"50.960","dur":"1.840","text":"meeting transcripts and then attach them"},{"start":"52.800","dur":"2.800","text":"into your CRM without actually reading"},{"start":"55.600","dur":"2.080","text":"the contents of the file. The"},{"start":"57.680","dur":"1.600","text":"architecture for this agent is pretty"},{"start":"59.280","dur":"1.840","text":"simple. It''s just one agent with this"},{"start":"61.120","dur":"2.079","text":"code execution tool that connects to"},{"start":"63.199","dur":"2.960","text":"Google Drive MCP and Notion MCP because"},{"start":"66.159","dur":"2.721","text":"our CRM is in notion. So in order to get"},{"start":"68.880","dur":"1.919","text":"started, you need to copy our starter"},{"start":"70.799","dur":"2.241","text":"template which will now contain a new"},{"start":"73.040","dur":"2.880","text":"special command to use this new pattern."},{"start":"75.920","dur":"1.920","text":"Make sure to set visibility to private"},{"start":"77.840","dur":"2.720","text":"and then open this repo in cursor. So I"},{"start":"80.560","dur":"2.000","text":"will be building this in cursor, but you"},{"start":"82.560","dur":"2.879","text":"can also use cloud codeex or any other"},{"start":"85.439","dur":"2.241","text":"AI coding agent that you prefer. The"},{"start":"87.680","dur":"1.280","text":"only thing you need to do if you''re not"},{"start":"88.960","dur":"2.560","text":"using cursor is to simply tag this"},{"start":"91.520","dur":"2.480","text":"workflow file and the commands files"},{"start":"94.000","dur":"2.320","text":"that we''ll be using in the prompt. So"},{"start":"96.320","dur":"1.839","text":"I''m going to start simple and just tell"},{"start":"98.159","dur":"2.801","text":"cloudset to create a sales ops agent"},{"start":"100.960","dur":"2.159","text":"with two built-in tools IPython"},{"start":"103.119","dur":"2.161","text":"interpreter and persistent shell tool."},{"start":"105.280","dur":"1.839","text":"The reason we need these two tools is"},{"start":"107.119","dur":"1.841","text":"because the agent must be able to"},{"start":"108.960","dur":"2.000","text":"actually discover local files and then"},{"start":"110.960","dur":"2.240","text":"run them in Python in order to use this"},{"start":"113.200","dur":"2.160","text":"new approach. And both of these tools"},{"start":"115.360","dur":"2.399","text":"are already available in our framework."},{"start":"117.759","dur":"2.000","text":"So let''s hit send and wait until the"},{"start":"119.759","dur":"2.000","text":"agent is built. Now, I''m also going to"},{"start":"121.759","dur":"2.640","text":"tell it to add another sales ops direct"},{"start":"124.399","dur":"2.961","text":"MCP agent for comparison later. By the"},{"start":"127.360","dur":"1.119","text":"way, if you''re building a more"},{"start":"128.479","dur":"2.321","text":"sophisticated MVP, there is also a new"},{"start":"130.800","dur":"2.320","text":"PRD command which you can use to have"},{"start":"133.120","dur":"2.479","text":"more control over your agent structure."},{"start":"135.599","dur":"1.601","text":"Okay, now here''s where the magic"},{"start":"137.200","dur":"2.480","text":"happens. I added a new special command"},{"start":"139.680","dur":"2.960","text":"called MCP code execution, which you can"},{"start":"142.640","dur":"3.200","text":"use to add MCP servers to an agent using"},{"start":"145.840","dur":"2.160","text":"this new pattern. So all you need to do"},{"start":"148.000","dur":"1.920","text":"in order to use this is simply tag this"},{"start":"149.920","dur":"2.640","text":"command and then tell cursor which MCP"},{"start":"152.560","dur":"2.319","text":"servers to use. So I recommend finding"},{"start":"154.879","dur":"2.561","text":"the exact MCP servers you need on GitHub"},{"start":"157.440","dur":"2.560","text":"or elsewhere and then adding links back"},{"start":"160.000","dur":"2.640","text":"into cursor. Now simply hit send again."},{"start":"162.640","dur":"1.760","text":"So this command already describes to"},{"start":"164.400","dur":"1.760","text":"cursor pretty much everything it needs"},{"start":"166.160","dur":"2.320","text":"to know about this new pattern and even"},{"start":"168.480","dur":"2.080","text":"links the blog post and all the other"},{"start":"170.560","dur":"1.920","text":"resources that it might need. This way"},{"start":"172.480","dur":"2.160","text":"cursor can reliably add it using the"},{"start":"174.640","dur":"1.840","text":"same structure that they proposed in"},{"start":"176.480","dur":"1.839","text":"this blog post. So you can see how now"},{"start":"178.319","dur":"2.241","text":"cursor created the server directory with"},{"start":"180.560","dur":"2.160","text":"the code for our servers and then it"},{"start":"182.720","dur":"1.680","text":"proceeds to creating the code for"},{"start":"184.400","dur":"2.479","text":"individual tools. You might also need to"},{"start":"186.879","dur":"2.321","text":"authenticate the server if it''s using or"},{"start":"189.200","dur":"2.080","text":"off. Now it proceeds to creating files"},{"start":"191.280","dur":"2.560","text":"for individual tools. So you can see how"},{"start":"193.840","dur":"3.119","text":"now this server is made here directly in"},{"start":"196.959","dur":"2.081","text":"code instead of passing this description"},{"start":"199.040","dur":"2.000","text":"and the arguments directly into the"},{"start":"201.040","dur":"2.640","text":"agents context window. Cursor saves this"},{"start":"203.680","dur":"2.479","text":"description in code. So then whenever"},{"start":"206.159","dur":"2.321","text":"our agent needs to use this tool, it"},{"start":"208.480","dur":"2.240","text":"will simply read this file and then it"},{"start":"210.720","dur":"2.320","text":"will see the whole description and the"},{"start":"213.040","dur":"2.400","text":"arguments in order to use this tool. So"},{"start":"215.440","dur":"1.680","text":"this way again we don''t load all the"},{"start":"217.120","dur":"2.560","text":"tools. We only load one tool that cursor"},{"start":"219.680","dur":"2.160","text":"actually needs to use. Okay. So in total"},{"start":"221.840","dur":"2.880","text":"cursor created 15 tools for notion MCP"},{"start":"224.720","dur":"2.239","text":"server and four tools for Google drive."},{"start":"226.959","dur":"2.321","text":"It has also already tested notion MCP"},{"start":"229.280","dur":"2.000","text":"server. However, it wasn''t able to test"},{"start":"231.280","dur":"1.360","text":"Google Drive because of missing"},{"start":"232.640","dur":"1.679","text":"credentials. So make sure you provide"},{"start":"234.319","dur":"1.761","text":"all the credentials up front. Do not"},{"start":"236.080","dur":"1.760","text":"repeat my mistake. Typically you can"},{"start":"237.840","dur":"1.599","text":"find instructions on how to get the"},{"start":"239.439","dur":"1.841","text":"credentials inside the readme of your"},{"start":"241.280","dur":"1.920","text":"MCP server. Then you can simply tell"},{"start":"243.200","dur":"2.239","text":"cursor to retest the server. Then you"},{"start":"245.439","dur":"2.321","text":"will also be required to authenticate."},{"start":"247.760","dur":"1.759","text":"Okay. Now the next step is to write"},{"start":"249.519","dur":"1.440","text":"instructions. So for writing"},{"start":"250.959","dur":"1.681","text":"instructions, I also recommend you use"},{"start":"252.640","dur":"2.080","text":"this write instructions command and then"},{"start":"254.720","dur":"2.000","text":"simply tag the agent that you want to"},{"start":"256.720","dur":"1.919","text":"create the instructions for. Then cursor"},{"start":"258.639","dur":"1.440","text":"is going to ask you a few questions to"},{"start":"260.079","dur":"2.000","text":"properly define the context for your"},{"start":"262.079","dur":"2.001","text":"agent. So make sure you answer all these"},{"start":"264.080","dur":"1.440","text":"questions carefully and the most"},{"start":"265.520","dur":"2.000","text":"important one is the process and"},{"start":"267.520","dur":"2.480","text":"workflow. So prompting is key with this"},{"start":"270.000","dur":"1.840","text":"technique and in order for this agent to"},{"start":"271.840","dur":"2.000","text":"use it effectively, it must clearly"},{"start":"273.840","dur":"2.079","text":"understand the process. So basically the"},{"start":"275.919","dur":"1.840","text":"first step is to always check available"},{"start":"277.759","dur":"2.401","text":"skills in the Mnt skills folder. I''ll"},{"start":"280.160","dur":"2.880","text":"explain why Mnt folder later then it"},{"start":"283.040","dur":"1.840","text":"should use the skill if such a skill is"},{"start":"284.880","dur":"2.400","text":"found for a specific task. If no skills"},{"start":"287.280","dur":"2.400","text":"are found then it should only read one"},{"start":"289.680","dur":"2.160","text":"tool that it needs to use and after that"},{"start":"291.840","dur":"2.079","text":"it should combine all such tools in"},{"start":"293.919","dur":"1.761","text":"order to complete a task successfully"},{"start":"295.680","dur":"2.160","text":"and finally provide suggestions for new"},{"start":"297.840","dur":"2.160","text":"skills to be added. So you can play"},{"start":"300.000","dur":"1.840","text":"around with this workflow. This is just"},{"start":"301.840","dur":"2.400","text":"a general process from the blog post."},{"start":"304.240","dur":"1.200","text":"But I think there are a lot of"},{"start":"305.440","dur":"1.759","text":"innovations just from prompting the"},{"start":"307.199","dur":"2.161","text":"agent. So let''s hit send. And in the"},{"start":"309.360","dur":"2.800","text":"meantime, I also want to add MCPS using"},{"start":"312.160","dur":"2.240","text":"the direct MCP approach to the other"},{"start":"314.400","dur":"3.120","text":"sales ops direct MCP agent. So for this,"},{"start":"317.520","dur":"2.160","text":"we also have a command. It''s simply add"},{"start":"319.680","dur":"1.760","text":"MCP. And then I''m also just going to"},{"start":"321.440","dur":"2.479","text":"link the two MCP servers that we added"},{"start":"323.919","dur":"2.401","text":"to the previous agent. Okay, now we are"},{"start":"326.320","dur":"2.080","text":"ready to test this agency. So let''s open"},{"start":"328.400","dur":"2.000","text":"it in terminal and just run python"},{"start":"330.400","dur":"3.040","text":"agency.py. Pi. Now let''s perform a"},{"start":"333.440","dur":"1.920","text":"simple test. Let me ask it what''s on"},{"start":"335.360","dur":"3.640","text":"this notion page."},{"start":"339.919","dur":"2.000","text":"So first the agent listed the mount"},{"start":"341.919","dur":"3.361","text":"skills directory. Then it read the fetch"},{"start":"345.280","dur":"1.680","text":"tool file to understand all the"},{"start":"346.960","dur":"2.239","text":"parameters. And it seems like it ran"},{"start":"349.199","dur":"3.601","text":"into some issues with the imports."},{"start":"352.800","dur":"1.839","text":"However, then at the end I was still"},{"start":"354.639","dur":"2.801","text":"able to read this page by performing"},{"start":"357.440","dur":"3.039","text":"this fetch tool request and it provided"},{"start":"360.479","dur":"3.041","text":"me with the preview of this file. Okay."},{"start":"363.520","dur":"1.440","text":"Now the next step is to deploy this"},{"start":"364.960","dur":"1.679","text":"agent and then we''ll compare it with the"},{"start":"366.639","dur":"2.321","text":"direct MCP approach. So let''s push our"},{"start":"368.960","dur":"2.160","text":"changes to GitHub and now let''s go to"},{"start":"371.120","dur":"2.560","text":"agency. So hit create new agency and"},{"start":"373.680","dur":"3.200","text":"then find this new agent repo. Then"},{"start":"376.880","dur":"2.240","text":"provide your keys from the end file. And"},{"start":"379.120","dur":"2.000","text":"now let''s wait until our agency is"},{"start":"381.120","dur":"2.400","text":"deployed. Okay. So now our agency is"},{"start":"383.520","dur":"2.480","text":"deployed. So let''s actually test it. So"},{"start":"386.000","dur":"2.479","text":"let me put it in a custom GPT. Let''s"},{"start":"388.479","dur":"2.720","text":"select both agents"},{"start":"391.199","dur":"2.000","text":"and let''s deploy it. Now let me send"},{"start":"393.199","dur":"2.720","text":"this task from Andropics blog post to"},{"start":"395.919","dur":"2.321","text":"copy the transcript from Google Drive"},{"start":"398.240","dur":"2.880","text":"and paste it into a page in notion."},{"start":"401.120","dur":"1.440","text":"Let''s see if it''s actually going to be"},{"start":"402.560","dur":"2.639","text":"able to do it."},{"start":"405.199","dur":"1.921","text":"Seems like it did read way too many"},{"start":"407.120","dur":"1.919","text":"files. Like for example, it even read"},{"start":"409.039","dur":"2.000","text":"this server file which it definitely"},{"start":"411.039","dur":"3.401","text":"doesn''t need."},{"start":"415.680","dur":"2.160","text":"And now finally it tells me that it was"},{"start":"417.840","dur":"2.720","text":"in fact able to do this. So let''s check"},{"start":"420.560","dur":"3.639","text":"the notion page."},{"start":"424.960","dur":"1.600","text":"And yes indeed we now get this"},{"start":"426.560","dur":"2.720","text":"transcript from our Q&A call exactly"},{"start":"429.280","dur":"2.800","text":"like it was on Google Drive. And also at"},{"start":"432.080","dur":"2.160","text":"the end it proposed to create this new"},{"start":"434.240","dur":"2.480","text":"skill for itself. So let me tell it to"},{"start":"436.720","dur":"1.840","text":"save the skill. So you can see that the"},{"start":"438.560","dur":"1.919","text":"agent told me that it saved the skills"},{"start":"440.479","dur":"2.560","text":"in the mount skills directory. So the"},{"start":"443.039","dur":"1.521","text":"reason you need to use this mount"},{"start":"444.560","dur":"1.520","text":"directory is because we now have"},{"start":"446.080","dur":"2.720","text":"persistent storage on our platform. And"},{"start":"448.800","dur":"1.600","text":"without this feature, it would not be"},{"start":"450.400","dur":"2.160","text":"possible to allow your agents to evolve"},{"start":"452.560","dur":"2.400","text":"and build their own skills over time. So"},{"start":"454.960","dur":"2.239","text":"in this mount directory essentially your"},{"start":"457.199","dur":"2.321","text":"agents can now save files like this and"},{"start":"459.520","dur":"2.160","text":"reference them across different chats."},{"start":"461.680","dur":"2.079","text":"So now if I start a new chat and then"},{"start":"463.759","dur":"2.160","text":"send the same prompt again, the agent"},{"start":"465.919","dur":"2.321","text":"should take a lot less time and just use"},{"start":"468.240","dur":"2.000","text":"the skill in order to do this task"},{"start":"470.240","dur":"2.079","text":"quickly. So you can see how now it found"},{"start":"472.319","dur":"2.481","text":"the skill and read the file and the"},{"start":"474.800","dur":"2.079","text":"agent was able to still perform the same"},{"start":"476.879","dur":"1.760","text":"task."},{"start":"478.639","dur":"2.000","text":"Okay, now let''s quickly test another"},{"start":"480.639","dur":"3.441","text":"agent that uses direct MCP approach. So"},{"start":"484.080","dur":"1.760","text":"now you can see how this agent is"},{"start":"485.840","dur":"1.840","text":"reading this whole transcript with the G"},{"start":"487.680","dur":"2.560","text":"drive read file tool which hopefully is"},{"start":"490.240","dur":"2.560","text":"not going to cost me too much and it"},{"start":"492.800","dur":"2.480","text":"also read the notion page and now it''s"},{"start":"495.280","dur":"1.919","text":"trying to add this transcript to this"},{"start":"497.199","dur":"2.081","text":"notion page. But as you can see it has"},{"start":"499.280","dur":"2.639","text":"to manually type this whole thing which"},{"start":"501.919","dur":"1.921","text":"is definitely going to cost me too much"},{"start":"503.840","dur":"2.880","text":"now. So you can see how it''s literally"},{"start":"506.720","dur":"2.000","text":"spending like probably tens of thousands"},{"start":"508.720","dur":"2.319","text":"of tokens for no reason simply because"},{"start":"511.039","dur":"2.560","text":"it had to do one simple copy paste"},{"start":"513.599","dur":"2.961","text":"operation. Finally, it''s finished. So"},{"start":"516.560","dur":"2.240","text":"now let''s take a look at the traces and"},{"start":"518.800","dur":"2.479","text":"analyze the costs. So tracing is enabled"},{"start":"521.279","dur":"2.320","text":"by default in our framework. And in"},{"start":"523.599","dur":"1.441","text":"order to see the traces, all you need to"},{"start":"525.040","dur":"2.160","text":"do is go to dashboard and then simply"},{"start":"527.200","dur":"2.720","text":"find the name of your agency. Okay, so"},{"start":"529.920","dur":"2.960","text":"let''s see this sales ops direct MCP"},{"start":"532.880","dur":"2.720","text":"agent. And in total, this agent consumed"},{"start":"535.600","dur":"3.679","text":"32,000 tokens. This is just insane. And"},{"start":"539.279","dur":"1.921","text":"most of these tokens aren''t even input"},{"start":"541.200","dur":"1.920","text":"tokens. It''s also a lot of output"},{"start":"543.120","dur":"2.240","text":"tokens, which are extremely expensive."},{"start":"545.360","dur":"1.599","text":"And with this new approach, the amount"},{"start":"546.959","dur":"3.440","text":"of tokens is only 12,000, which is a lot"},{"start":"550.399","dur":"2.321","text":"less, although it''s still quite a bit."},{"start":"552.720","dur":"1.440","text":"And I think the reason this is still"},{"start":"554.160","dur":"1.920","text":"consumes so many tokens is because this"},{"start":"556.080","dur":"2.319","text":"agent, as you can see, just performs way"},{"start":"558.399","dur":"2.481","text":"too many unnecessary tool calls. But I"},{"start":"560.880","dur":"1.680","text":"do think that it''s completely possible"},{"start":"562.560","dur":"2.719","text":"to optimize it with more prompting. And"},{"start":"565.279","dur":"2.161","text":"when the agent used one of the existing"},{"start":"567.440","dur":"3.200","text":"skills, it only consumed 4,000 tokens to"},{"start":"570.640","dur":"2.160","text":"perform the same task, which is now"},{"start":"572.800","dur":"3.520","text":"around 10 times less. So in conclusion,"},{"start":"575.000","dur":"113.000"},{"start":"576.320","dur":"2.160","text":"I believe this approach is extremely"},{"start":"578.480","dur":"2.479","text":"powerful, but as they say, with great"},{"start":"580.959","dur":"2.721","text":"power comes great responsibility. While"},{"start":"583.680","dur":"1.680","text":"I was definitely able to reduce the"},{"start":"585.360","dur":"1.840","text":"token consumption from the intermediate"},{"start":"587.200","dur":"2.480","text":"tool outputs, the agent still consumed"},{"start":"589.680","dur":"1.839","text":"more tokens than it should have when"},{"start":"591.519","dur":"2.801","text":"calling the tools. It executed code way"},{"start":"594.320","dur":"1.840","text":"too many times. It read way too many"},{"start":"596.160","dur":"2.000","text":"unnecessary files and it just took too"},{"start":"598.160","dur":"1.840","text":"long to perform a simple task on the"},{"start":"600.000","dur":"2.480","text":"first attempt. However, the agent was"},{"start":"602.480","dur":"2.240","text":"still able to save a lot more tokens"},{"start":"604.720","dur":"2.880","text":"compared to the old direct MCP approach."},{"start":"607.600","dur":"1.760","text":"Additionally, it was even able to"},{"start":"609.360","dur":"2.400","text":"self-improve by creating a new skill"},{"start":"611.760","dur":"1.759","text":"which cut down the number of code"},{"start":"613.519","dur":"3.041","text":"executions in subsequent runs. So, my"},{"start":"616.560","dur":"2.800","text":"final verdict is yes, this approach is"},{"start":"619.360","dur":"2.080","text":"ready for production, but it requires"},{"start":"621.440","dur":"3.200","text":"proper prompting. Prompting here is key."},{"start":"624.640","dur":"2.160","text":"While the LLMs aren''t trained for this"},{"start":"626.800","dur":"2.000","text":"new method yet, you have to carefully"},{"start":"628.800","dur":"2.159","text":"describe how to use this new pattern,"},{"start":"630.959","dur":"1.601","text":"otherwise they''re going to make a lot of"},{"start":"632.560","dur":"2.160","text":"mistakes. But if you do it right, and"},{"start":"634.720","dur":"1.600","text":"I''m sure many of you will, with this"},{"start":"636.320","dur":"2.400","text":"repo, the benefits far outweigh the"},{"start":"638.720","dur":"2.239","text":"costs. You get way more autonomy and"},{"start":"640.959","dur":"2.721","text":"flexibility with only a minor drop in"},{"start":"643.680","dur":"2.719","text":"reliability. So yes, this is the new"},{"start":"646.399","dur":"2.721","text":"paradigm. Just let your agents run the"},{"start":"649.120","dur":"3.040","text":"code. We no longer have to create these"},{"start":"652.160","dur":"1.280","text":"abstractions on top of other"},{"start":"653.440","dur":"2.000","text":"abstractions because agents can just"},{"start":"655.440","dur":"2.160","text":"generate the code to do whatever they"},{"start":"657.600","dur":"2.720","text":"need by themselves. However, don''t use"},{"start":"660.320","dur":"1.840","text":"it for simple agents like customer"},{"start":"662.160","dur":"2.400","text":"support. save it for more sophisticated"},{"start":"664.560","dur":"2.719","text":"general agents like analytics, research,"},{"start":"667.279","dur":"2.481","text":"or operations. For simple agents, it"},{"start":"669.760","dur":"1.519","text":"still doesn''t make sense. And when"},{"start":"671.279","dur":"1.601","text":"you''re ready to deploy this, check out"},{"start":"672.880","dur":"1.840","text":"our platform because infrastructure"},{"start":"674.720","dur":"1.600","text":"overhead is actually the biggest"},{"start":"676.320","dur":"2.240","text":"downside of this approach. And we''re the"},{"start":"678.560","dur":"1.600","text":"only platform on the market that"},{"start":"680.160","dur":"1.919","text":"supports everything you need to run this"},{"start":"682.079","dur":"2.241","text":"out of the box. More advanced EI agent"},{"start":"684.320","dur":"1.519","text":"templates are coming on this channel"},{"start":"685.839","dur":"2.560","text":"soon."}]}}','2025-11-13T21:21:41.453Z');
INSERT INTO "mcp_actions" VALUES('570bc0f9-5a1b-41a5-9d10-53534eea3a83','5dd28c5e-208f-4d10-902c-c6eb0fd17f10','youtube-transcript','get_youtube_transcript',3,1,NULL,NULL,'{"params":{"videoUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BOl05zmQjOg"},"result":{"data":[{"start":"0.240","dur":"1.680","text":"What is the future of the product cycle"},{"start":"1.920","dur":"2.320","text":"with AI? This is a question I get asked"},{"start":"4.240","dur":"2.559","text":"all the time with product teams. Hey, my"},{"start":"6.799","dur":"1.760","text":"name is Diane and I''m the founder of the"},{"start":"8.559","dur":"2.241","text":"design project. I have designed for"},{"start":"10.800","dur":"2.640","text":"Crocs and MercedesBenz. I''ve been a solo"},{"start":"13.440","dur":"2.880","text":"designer for five startups and today we"},{"start":"16.320","dur":"2.959","text":"work with over 50 B2B SAS companies"},{"start":"19.279","dur":"1.201","text":"working with teams that have been"},{"start":"20.480","dur":"2.000","text":"acquired by Slack, Nvidia, and Mr."},{"start":"22.480","dur":"2.080","text":"Beast. I''m on the cutting edge of"},{"start":"24.560","dur":"2.000","text":"speeding up design to dev handoff using"},{"start":"26.560","dur":"2.639","text":"AI to generate front-end code. Today, I"},{"start":"29.199","dur":"2.240","text":"take my Figma designs, I build front-end"},{"start":"31.439","dur":"2.001","text":"code with cloud code and cursor, and I"},{"start":"33.440","dur":"2.560","text":"deliver directly into my customers repo."},{"start":"36.000","dur":"2.160","text":"What we''ll cover today, setting up cloud"},{"start":"38.160","dur":"2.399","text":"code with cursor, connecting GitHub and"},{"start":"40.559","dur":"2.881","text":"Figma MCP. We''re going to build out a"},{"start":"43.440","dur":"2.400","text":"feature within cloud code and cursor,"},{"start":"45.840","dur":"1.920","text":"and I''m going to answer questions I get"},{"start":"47.760","dur":"1.600","text":"from teams that want to implement this"},{"start":"49.360","dur":"2.800","text":"process. So, why claude code within"},{"start":"52.160","dur":"3.360","text":"cursor? I have tested Figma make, v0,"},{"start":"55.520","dur":"2.800","text":"lovable, all of them. This is my only"},{"start":"58.320","dur":"2.079","text":"recommendation. Figma to claude code"},{"start":"60.399","dur":"2.800","text":"within cursor. Why? Because claude code"},{"start":"63.199","dur":"2.319","text":"is better. It cuts out the middleman and"},{"start":"65.519","dur":"2.001","text":"it goes directly into the codebase that"},{"start":"67.520","dur":"3.040","text":"your devs are using. Okay. Step one is"},{"start":"70.560","dur":"3.120","text":"get repo access. Your designers, PMs,"},{"start":"73.680","dur":"1.840","text":"anyone on the product team needs to get"},{"start":"75.520","dur":"1.760","text":"invited to the company repo from your"},{"start":"77.280","dur":"2.720","text":"devs. The biggest concern here is devs"},{"start":"80.000","dur":"2.799","text":"say, \"I don''t want my designer PM"},{"start":"82.799","dur":"2.161","text":"messing up my code.\" Which is completely"},{"start":"84.960","dur":"1.920","text":"valid. The solution is to create a"},{"start":"86.880","dur":"1.360","text":"separate branch that the product team"},{"start":"88.240","dur":"1.600","text":"can work off of. They work off this"},{"start":"89.840","dur":"1.680","text":"branch. They won''t break the code and"},{"start":"91.520","dur":"2.720","text":"there''s peace of mind. So now let''s get"},{"start":"94.240","dur":"1.760","text":"started. Here''s the server up and"},{"start":"96.000","dur":"1.520","text":"running."},{"start":"97.520","dur":"2.320","text":"Here''s cloud code within cursor. And"},{"start":"99.840","dur":"2.400","text":"here''s my Figma file."},{"start":"102.240","dur":"2.000","text":"First, I''m going to make sure it has"},{"start":"104.240","dur":"6.280","text":"access. Do you see my Figma?"},{"start":"110.640","dur":"2.960","text":"Do you see my Figma?"},{"start":"113.600","dur":"3.760","text":"Now, what I need to do is build a button"},{"start":"117.360","dur":"2.480","text":"here that is going to open the sidebar I"},{"start":"119.840","dur":"5.000","text":"created. I''m going to prompt it"},{"start":"125.520","dur":"1.760","text":"create a button that looks like this"},{"start":"127.280","dur":"1.920","text":"button class and put it next to this"},{"start":"129.200","dur":"1.759","text":"button class. So, basically I''m telling"},{"start":"130.959","dur":"1.761","text":"it create a button that looks exactly"},{"start":"132.720","dur":"2.879","text":"like this next to this button. Let''s see"},{"start":"135.599","dur":"3.481","text":"what it does."},{"start":"139.440","dur":"4.000","text":"the button next to the call actions"},{"start":"143.440","dur":"1.519","text":"button."},{"start":"144.959","dur":"2.000","text":"Both buttons visible side by side. I"},{"start":"146.959","dur":"2.881","text":"should keep both buttons replaced. Keep"},{"start":"149.840","dur":"3.560","text":"both buttons."},{"start":"154.879","dur":"2.720","text":"Okay, here we go. Add context. I would"},{"start":"157.599","dur":"2.081","text":"need to clean this up, make it"},{"start":"159.680","dur":"1.680","text":"capitalized, but it added the button,"},{"start":"161.360","dur":"2.480","text":"which is great. Okay, now I''m going to"},{"start":"163.840","dur":"1.920","text":"prompt it."},{"start":"165.760","dur":"1.920","text":"Based on my Figma selection, create a"},{"start":"167.680","dur":"1.520","text":"sidebar that slides out from the right"},{"start":"169.200","dur":"1.600","text":"side of the screen when clicking the add"},{"start":"170.800","dur":"2.560","text":"context button. Make sure all fonts and"},{"start":"173.360","dur":"2.000","text":"colors adhere to the design. For all"},{"start":"175.360","dur":"1.760","text":"components, make sure each state is"},{"start":"177.120","dur":"1.600","text":"fully functional. Make sure to follow"},{"start":"178.720","dur":"1.519","text":"the exact programming language the"},{"start":"180.239","dur":"2.881","text":"codebase already uses. So what''s really"},{"start":"183.120","dur":"2.240","text":"important here is to start to build a"},{"start":"185.360","dur":"2.080","text":"design system because once you build a"},{"start":"187.440","dur":"2.400","text":"design system, it is going to be able to"},{"start":"189.840","dur":"2.000","text":"replicate those components and reuse"},{"start":"191.840","dur":"2.000","text":"them everywhere and you won''t have to"},{"start":"193.840","dur":"1.679","text":"keep tweaking because it is already"},{"start":"195.519","dur":"2.000","text":"pulling the direct code that you''ve"},{"start":"197.519","dur":"3.000","text":"created."},{"start":"200.800","dur":"1.519","text":"Okay,"},{"start":"202.319","dur":"3.801","text":"let''s go check it out."},{"start":"208.560","dur":"3.840","text":"Let''s see how it looks compared to this."},{"start":"212.400","dur":"2.960","text":"Pretty good,"},{"start":"215.360","dur":"3.000","text":"functional."},{"start":"218.400","dur":"2.399","text":"So, there you have it. Built this whole"},{"start":"220.799","dur":"2.481","text":"sidebar connecting to the button with"},{"start":"223.280","dur":"2.000","text":"prompting."},{"start":"225.280","dur":"2.000","text":"Great. Now, the last thing I want to do"},{"start":"227.280","dur":"5.239","text":"is commit this code."},{"start":"235.120","dur":"2.880","text":"So, I''m going to go up here,"},{"start":"238.000","dur":"2.319","text":"press commit. It''s going to be pushed to"},{"start":"240.319","dur":"3.280","text":"the repo for the devs to review. Great."},{"start":"243.599","dur":"2.401","text":"Done. Here are the most common questions"},{"start":"246.000","dur":"2.239","text":"I get from founders, PMs, head of"},{"start":"248.239","dur":"2.560","text":"product that want to start this process."},{"start":"250.799","dur":"2.241","text":"Question one, what percentage does a"},{"start":"253.040","dur":"2.080","text":"design need to be done before passing it"},{"start":"255.120","dur":"3.519","text":"to code? I would say about 80 to 90%"},{"start":"258.639","dur":"2.160","text":"done. It doesn''t need interactions. It"},{"start":"260.799","dur":"1.921","text":"just needs the components and the layout"},{"start":"262.720","dur":"2.560","text":"on the screen because cloud code is not"},{"start":"265.280","dur":"2.800","text":"a mind readader. So by taking that Figma"},{"start":"268.080","dur":"1.600","text":"design, you''re going to be able to get"},{"start":"269.680","dur":"2.400","text":"it to a place where cloud code can pick"},{"start":"272.080","dur":"1.440","text":"it up, start to build those"},{"start":"273.520","dur":"1.760","text":"interactions, and then from there you"},{"start":"275.280","dur":"2.479","text":"can tweak as necessary."},{"start":"277.759","dur":"2.160","text":"Question two, once designs are"},{"start":"279.919","dur":"1.681","text":"implemented, what does that iteration"},{"start":"281.600","dur":"2.400","text":"cycle look like? So the designers can"},{"start":"284.000","dur":"1.919","text":"continue to prompt and work within cloud"},{"start":"285.919","dur":"2.401","text":"code and cursor or they can go back to"},{"start":"288.320","dur":"3.040","text":"Figma. It''s dependent on the project. I"},{"start":"291.360","dur":"2.720","text":"suggest if it''s already in cloud code,"},{"start":"294.080","dur":"1.839","text":"you continue to prompt it there to get"},{"start":"295.919","dur":"2.401","text":"it to where you need. This process takes"},{"start":"298.320","dur":"2.879","text":"some time. There is a learning curve. So"},{"start":"301.199","dur":"2.000","text":"just suggest to your team is to stick"},{"start":"303.199","dur":"2.161","text":"with it. Question three, can I trust the"},{"start":"305.360","dur":"2.640","text":"code? This is why I suggest cloud code"},{"start":"308.000","dur":"2.800","text":"because it is the code that most dev"},{"start":"310.800","dur":"3.360","text":"teams are using to build on top of. I"},{"start":"314.160","dur":"2.080","text":"also suggest that engineers still review"},{"start":"316.240","dur":"2.160","text":"the PRD. They need to check for"},{"start":"318.400","dur":"2.079","text":"performance, code standards, security,"},{"start":"320.479","dur":"2.481","text":"everything like that. Again, this is"},{"start":"322.960","dur":"2.720","text":"really great for front-end code."},{"start":"325.680","dur":"3.280","text":"Backend, I still suggest that the devs"},{"start":"328.960","dur":"2.320","text":"play with the back end. Question four,"},{"start":"331.280","dur":"1.919","text":"what''s the designer''s workload versus"},{"start":"333.199","dur":"1.840","text":"AI''s workload? Are designers just"},{"start":"335.039","dur":"2.801","text":"pressing buttons? Now, no. Designers are"},{"start":"337.840","dur":"2.320","text":"still thinking deeply about the UX and"},{"start":"340.160","dur":"2.080","text":"the process up front. They''re still"},{"start":"342.240","dur":"1.920","text":"putting together those Figma designs."},{"start":"344.160","dur":"2.160","text":"They''re using AI for research."},{"start":"346.320","dur":"1.760","text":"absolutely as they should to speed"},{"start":"348.080","dur":"2.640","text":"things up. But once they get that Figma"},{"start":"350.720","dur":"2.240","text":"in place, they basically are able to"},{"start":"352.960","dur":"2.480","text":"replace that front-end dev that you"},{"start":"355.440","dur":"2.080","text":"need. The designer is still designing,"},{"start":"357.520","dur":"2.080","text":"they''re also shipping, and AI is an"},{"start":"359.600","dur":"3.120","text":"execution tool, not the brain. So, thank"},{"start":"362.720","dur":"1.759","text":"you for watching my video. Please"},{"start":"364.479","dur":"1.681","text":"subscribe to the channel to get more"},{"start":"366.160","dur":"3.120","text":"insights from product teams."}]}}','2025-11-13T21:36:41.638Z');
INSERT INTO "mcp_actions" VALUES('cc704a5b-4dfe-48fe-974d-ed1d9528a187','5dd28c5e-208f-4d10-902c-c6eb0fd17f10','youtube-transcript','get_youtube_transcript',3,1,NULL,NULL,'{"params":{"videoUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GuyZspG3-Po"},"result":{"data":[{"start":"0.080","dur":"2.400","text":"Hey guys, welcome back to the channel."},{"start":"2.480","dur":"2.720","text":"Today we''re diving into an insane new AI"},{"start":"5.200","dur":"4.240","text":"tool, Z.AI chat, powered by the GLM 4.6"},{"start":"9.440","dur":"3.279","text":"and GLM 4.5 models. This platform is"},{"start":"12.719","dur":"2.401","text":"absolutely loaded with features. You can"},{"start":"15.120","dur":"2.159","text":"create AI powered slides to instantly"},{"start":"17.279","dur":"2.641","text":"generate professional PPTs, and it even"},{"start":"19.920","dur":"2.320","text":"comes with ready-made templates and HTML"},{"start":"22.240","dur":"1.760","text":"code output."},{"start":"24.000","dur":"2.160","text":"Next up, the magic design option lets"},{"start":"26.160","dur":"2.160","text":"you create stunning social media banners"},{"start":"28.320","dur":"3.520","text":"and post designs in seconds."},{"start":"31.840","dur":"1.920","text":"There''s also a deep research mode and a"},{"start":"33.760","dur":"2.880","text":"codewriting feature for developers."},{"start":"36.640","dur":"2.000","text":"And the highlight, you can even build"},{"start":"38.640","dur":"2.000","text":"full stack applications using the full"},{"start":"40.640","dur":"2.960","text":"stack option just like lovable or bolt."},{"start":"43.600","dur":"2.240","text":"The best part, it''s completely free and"},{"start":"45.840","dur":"3.039","text":"open source. I''ll select the full stack"},{"start":"48.879","dur":"2.641","text":"option and paste my prompt here. I''m"},{"start":"51.520","dur":"2.080","text":"building an Excel to JSON converter"},{"start":"53.600","dur":"2.000","text":"website with database integration and"},{"start":"55.600","dur":"2.080","text":"authentication. Just hit the submit"},{"start":"57.680","dur":"3.840","text":"button. The GLM 4.6 model is analyzing"},{"start":"61.520","dur":"2.240","text":"our prompt and setting up the project."},{"start":"63.760","dur":"2.480","text":"You can see it''s using Nex.js, Tailwind"},{"start":"66.240","dur":"3.280","text":"CSS, shed CN UI, and Prisma with SQL"},{"start":"69.520","dur":"2.320","text":"light setup as well. Now, it has created"},{"start":"71.840","dur":"2.160","text":"a to-do list and it''s executing each"},{"start":"74.000","dur":"2.479","text":"step one by one. The first to-do is"},{"start":"76.479","dur":"2.640","text":"installing the Excel SX library which is"},{"start":"79.119","dur":"2.241","text":"used to read Excel files. See, it"},{"start":"81.360","dur":"2.000","text":"started installing and now it has moved"},{"start":"83.360","dur":"2.160","text":"on to the next task, updating the Prisma"},{"start":"85.520","dur":"3.200","text":"schema. That one''s completed, too. Next,"},{"start":"88.720","dur":"1.920","text":"it''s moving to the to-do for building"},{"start":"90.640","dur":"2.479","text":"the main page UI design. It''s super"},{"start":"93.119","dur":"2.000","text":"fast. Now, only tasks number five and"},{"start":"95.119","dur":"1.921","text":"six are pending. We just need to wait a"},{"start":"97.040","dur":"2.079","text":"few seconds for them to finish. You can"},{"start":"99.119","dur":"1.921","text":"see the website preview appearing now."},{"start":"101.040","dur":"1.920","text":"And look at that. All the to-dos are"},{"start":"102.960","dur":"2.080","text":"completed. Now, it''s checking for any"},{"start":"105.040","dur":"2.000","text":"ESLint issues. So, let''s wait a few"},{"start":"107.040","dur":"2.480","text":"seconds again. And done. The website is"},{"start":"109.520","dur":"2.480","text":"now fully completed. It has created a"},{"start":"112.000","dur":"2.320","text":"file upload interface, file conversion"},{"start":"114.320","dur":"2.079","text":"functionality, and several other useful"},{"start":"116.399","dur":"2.641","text":"features as well. You can see it''s"},{"start":"119.040","dur":"3.200","text":"running on NextJS15 with TypeScript. For"},{"start":"122.240","dur":"2.479","text":"now, it''s using SQLite by default, but"},{"start":"124.719","dur":"1.921","text":"we can switch to Superbase later if"},{"start":"126.640","dur":"2.319","text":"needed. This is the folder structure it"},{"start":"128.959","dur":"1.601","text":"generated. Before checking out the"},{"start":"130.560","dur":"1.920","text":"website, let''s take a look at the code."},{"start":"132.480","dur":"2.800","text":"Click on the code preview toggle button."},{"start":"135.280","dur":"2.560","text":"Here''s the SQL database setup. Prisma"},{"start":"137.840","dur":"2.240","text":"with an example schema and the Nex.js"},{"start":"140.080","dur":"2.720","text":"app router code all neatly organized."},{"start":"142.800","dur":"1.600","text":"The folder structure is completely"},{"start":"144.400","dur":"1.919","text":"professional. And finally, there''s the"},{"start":"146.319","dur":"3.441","text":"shad CN components JSON file. The best"},{"start":"149.760","dur":"2.400","text":"part, you can download the entire"},{"start":"152.160","dur":"2.320","text":"project source code. That''s awesome. You"},{"start":"154.480","dur":"1.680","text":"can even modify it as you like and"},{"start":"156.160","dur":"2.400","text":"deploy it anywhere. Now we can check the"},{"start":"158.560","dur":"2.160","text":"website. We''re able to open it in a new"},{"start":"160.720","dur":"3.040","text":"tab easily and see everything clearly."},{"start":"163.760","dur":"1.839","text":"Let''s test it. I''ll upload a sample"},{"start":"165.599","dur":"2.401","text":"Excel file here and click submit. It"},{"start":"168.000","dur":"2.319","text":"instantly generates the JSON output. You"},{"start":"1